channel.title: Fishy spots?
channel.description: Hi, i haves a question (:D). If i make a fishing spot, does it have to be in water, or can it be on land, and make it able to give something other than fish (code for *COOKED* manta ray tht you can eat)

item.title: Fishy spots?
item.dc:creator: @_Rich Rich
item.description:
@_Rich wrote:

o.O O.o:

The addItem can be whatever you want. But it should just be an object, so theoretically I’d see it on land as well.

The original fishing spots are npcs, although there are other fishing spots that are objects as well.
